the Pope call him?

245
00:15:54,175 --> 00:15:56,342
Because the Pope was looking for
the best guy he could find...

246
00:15:56,508 --> 00:15:57,967
...to paint the ceiling
of his church in Rome.

247
00:15:58,175 --> 00:15:59,843
It don't sound like
that big a job, Father.

248
00:16:00,135 --> 00:16:01,469
Well, for Michelangelo it was.

249
00:16:01,927 --> 00:16:03,719
