as anything we had ever done.

428
00:25:09,808 --> 00:25:11,976
We were to hold the cart on the top
edge of the stairwell,

429
00:25:12,059 --> 00:25:14,310
Leaning it downward,
and wait for the vendor.

430
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:16,437
