he grabbed the handles.

431
00:25:16,603 --> 00:25:19,772
Then we'd leave the scene as he struggled
to ease the cart back onto the sidewalk.

432
00:25:20,355 --> 00:25:22,522
To this day, I don't
know why we did it.

